summary: So, yesterday I went to a family gathering and I was talking to my cousin (she’s 15, I’m 20) and I ask her about the music she’s...
body:
So, yesterday I went to a family gathering and I was talking to my cousin (she’s 15, I’m 20) and I ask her about the music she’s listening to, what kids these days are into, right?

And she says: “I’m really into oldschool music. Like there’s this song I’m obsessed with it goes like ‘she wears short skirts, I wear t-shirts, she’s cheer captain and….’ it’s amazing.”

And I just sat there. Smiling. Thinking: wow. FearlessTaylor Swift is oldschool to my cousin.

I’m getting old. I’m-

summary: One thing to keep in mind if you're traveling via car to Rep Tour Arlington, is the OU-Texas game, and the State Fair of Texas,...
body:
One thing to keep in mind if you’re traveling via car to Rep Tour Arlington, is the OU-Texas game, and the State Fair of Texas, Saturday. It’s going to be bananas, traffic wise. There can be on avg 80K people going there Saturday, roughly 75K on Friday. Add the game, and you get the idea. I realize the time of the game and the concert start are different, but keep it in mind.

They are separated by start time and distance, but traffic is still bad in Arlington. I’d recommend the Waze app. It’s worked for me, but it doesn’t seem to give directions for trips greater than 1000 miles. I hope they fixed that.

@taylorswift @taylornation @burningallthewitcheslightmeup

summary: How has it been FOUR YEARS since the Rhode Island Secret Session for 1989?! My life was forever changed. I’ve been a fan since...
body:
How has it been FOUR YEARS since the Rhode Island Secret Session for 1989?! My life was forever changed. I’ve been a fan since “Tim McGraw,” when I saw you opening for Rascal Flatts at the Meadows in Hartford, CT. I think that’s what I wrote about in a contest entry for the 1989 livestream, but you saved me for the secret sessions. I don’t know how I was so lucky. I’ve met some truly amazing people through you and we have been supporting you together since that day.

Happy friendiversary, @taylorswift.
